Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:39.84,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Slowly, quietly, floating by
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:48.52,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}Gently fading into the distant bright sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:57.40,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}More fickle than the wind,\N my goal is beyond it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:00.49,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Let's go together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:06.12,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a breath and skip along,\N the world's spring breath
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:11.75,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun brings all our smiles together
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.75,0:01:19.22,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Between "good morning" and "good bye" it's just us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.22,0:01:22.85,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}We can do whatever we want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.05,0:01:28.98,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}The sunlight shining down,\N a brand new sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.98,0:01:34.73,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning arch we promised to meet at
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.73,0:01:42.53,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}Waving your hand at me,\N let me make today a special day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:45.66,a-ch OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,600)}Let's start by talking
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.33,0:20:03.84,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,After school, with nothing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:08.68,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's raining
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:11.31,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to my place
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:19.15,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't usually say what you really think
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.15,0:20:23.03,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm sure I'll know today
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:29.16,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you smile
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:39.04,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to hide away there
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.04,0:20:42.96,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come a little closer
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:46.63,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a friend of mine
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:54.72,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Every season that passes by, now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.72,0:20:58.44,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, stay close by me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:04.44,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be with you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:12.28,a-ch insert,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to smile with you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.58,0:22:45.75,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,0)}Next to me in the sunset, a silhouette tall as me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.75,0:22:53.68,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the end of another fun day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.55,0:23:01.73,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I've still got so much unending stuff to talk about
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.73,0:23:09.07,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's time for us to go home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.07,0:23:16.24,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, I'll text you later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:23.54,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's page is about all our smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:30.84,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, see you tomorrow, thanks as always
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:39.41,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy we could be together today too
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:46.56,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Humhumhum, the wind and my heart are humming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.56,0:23:53.82,a-ch ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,100)}At the next corner, I'll turn around and say "Bye bye"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.59,0:00:04.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:05.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru-chan is waiting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:08.56,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:12.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't forgotten anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:14.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:16.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.01,0:00:19.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. Bye now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.24,0:00:21.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:24.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:59.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad6\fs70\4a&H74&\fad(400,0)\c&HFAE8D3&\pos(447,261)}Rainy {\c&HF9D9BE&}Days {\c&HFCD0A9&}are {\c&HF9BD8E&}for {\c&HF3B484&}Baths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:07.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:11.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I sent you a text about it after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:14.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? I didn't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.27,0:02:17.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:20.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your sock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.84,0:02:24.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot to put one of them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:28.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:33.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather go without any on than this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ru-Ru-Ru-Ru-Run-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo-Yo-Yo-Yo-Yo-Your...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,panties...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:59.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the things—how could I not notice?! How could I not notice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.96,0:03:02.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't squat! You can see from the front!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.33,0:03:05.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But was that the only reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.16,0:03:07.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.40,0:03:08.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this kind of thing normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:10.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone forgets things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not usually their panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:15.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.62,0:03:20.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just thought "But not usually their panties," didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:20.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:22.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ru—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've sure got it rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:41.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, I just can't handle mornings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.73,0:03:44.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always so sleepy, I completely space out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:45.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wearing them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh—right, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:54.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I thought maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:56.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.37,0:03:57.42,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:02.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I copy your notes from yesterday afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You left early yesterday, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.28,0:04:06.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:11.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lifesaver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What language is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. It's Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:22.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started falling asleep during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's not just mornings!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:27.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's kind of messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:29.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's anything you can't read, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.79,0:04:41.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:45.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuuko-chan, can I copy it after you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.90,0:04:49.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. After you're done, give it to Run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.36,0:04:50.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:58.35,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, are you nearsighted? What's your prescription?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,2.0.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Then why do you always wear them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm not wearing them...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see things...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:10.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I don't need to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.89,0:05:14.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:18.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Right behind you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:22.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.23,0:05:23.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.74,0:05:25.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're fun to scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a bit nearsighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:36.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, don't do that! I can't stand scary stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:40.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scared me for a second there, too! Nagi-chan, you put on a good act!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.77,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should join the drama club!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:45.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a ghost member.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:01.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I received two or three letters from you this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.85,0:06:10.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I remember rightly, it was in your second letter that you asked me to help you find a suitable post.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:09.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to the bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.19,0:06:13.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:22.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot. I can't say I need to go to the bathroom. It's too embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:26.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a headache...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.41,0:06:28.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, that's your stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.11,0:06:38.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go to the bathroom, so can I go after taking Yuuko-chan to the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:40.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:41.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.96,0:06:43.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:45.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.75,0:06:51.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Run. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:54.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it. I need to go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you need to go to the bathroom, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nurse's office...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:12.54,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! What's wrong? Are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. I feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I might have come down with someth—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:19.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to throw up...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:21.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, no, nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:24.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toi—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:26.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,To—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,To—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.83,0:07:28.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,To—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.37,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, that's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(200,0)\c&H423D37&\bord0}Nurse's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:44.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:47.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run suddenly fainted!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nurse isn't here today, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:54.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.65,0:07:56.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We could call in a teacher or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.78,0:07:59.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:25.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H0B1709&\c&H3C574E&}Let's keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:33.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's raining...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.33,0:08:35.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.74,0:08:37.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.11,0:08:38.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun was shining this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:41.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty light. It might be okay if we run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:45.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there, Tooru. Watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just learned this recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.33,0:08:54.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a rain goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.96,0:08:56.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to get wet to show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:57.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come back under here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:03.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be more careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's looking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:18.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan is completely soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:20.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.21,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:23.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:31.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.24,0:09:37.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad I work at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\bord0\c&H837E7C&\1a&H74&}Turn permission\N forms for camp\N in to every\N teacher or Yamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\fs40\bord0\1a&H74&\c&HB2A499&\pos(1114,363)}Too much\N work...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to dry Run-chan off fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:46.47,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! They're done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.52,0:09:55.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we don't need an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:58.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of embarrassing to wear these at this age...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:01.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fine in elementary school, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.62,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pair look is kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.62,0:10:07.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe just one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:09.75,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:13.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'll take mine off, then. I'm already wet anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.27,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}No, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.42,0:10:17.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan! Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:23.51,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.30,0:10:31.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! We were wondering what you were doing—\N Run, you're completely soaked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:34.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My place is close by. We can dry you off there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.64,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.30,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.71,0:10:44.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow. Is there a rain goddess in our school or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.71,0:10:48.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of rough, but we could just make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.70,0:10:54.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're all wet, then there's nothing to fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.81,0:10:58.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it's just to Nagi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.31,0:10:59.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much of a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to get wet. I'll call a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what high school students do!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:10.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it'll stop soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:13.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'd call a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:14.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan's place is this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:17.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.36,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I'm coming too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:22.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:25.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't leave me behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:31.12,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rain brings with it melancholy,\N but they're having fun regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:35.08,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.87,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H060606&\3c&HE5E5E5&\fs36\fad(200,0)}The smile\N you made\N as you ran\N through the rain\N was just\N so beautiful,\N I
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H060606&\3c&HE5E5E5&\fs36\fad(200,0)}No matter\N how hard the rain,\N no matter\N how thick the clouds,\N no matter how sharp
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6\pos(1104,480)\c&H060606&\3c&HE5E5E5&\fs36\fad(200,0)}I shall not\N hide a sun\N like you.\N No—\Neven if I were to try,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H060606&\3c&HE5E5E5&\fs36\fad(1000,0)}Kitou-Sensei
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.97,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\c&H060606&\3c&HE5E5E5&\fs36\fad(1000,0)}Hobby:\N Poetry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(277,49)\c&H010101&\3c&HFAFAFA&\bord4\fad(0,200)}Poetry
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.59,0:11:50.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\pos(986,49)\c&HFAFAFA&\3c&H010101&\bord4\fad(200,0)}Reality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:54.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, head on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to take a bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Aniki's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:07.07,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, you have a brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:14.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan! I have friends over right now, so don't use the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:21.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you call your brother "Aniki" or "Onii-chan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:23.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call him "Aniki"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.53,0:12:25.84,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.84,0:12:29.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our bath only fits two people at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:32.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make two pairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.48,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, rock, paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:38.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go in with Run first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:40.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.53,0:12:42.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's change now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.19,0:12:45.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.04,0:13:09.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it, I've never talked with Tooru alone before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:13.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.86,0:13:17.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The silence in situations like this is... just too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:20.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:22.06,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:24.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to watch something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:27.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of DVDs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.23,0:13:28.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.66,0:13:36.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really Real Scary Urban Legends, or the silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:39.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,A death and death decision?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your clothes over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.94,0:13:45.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.65,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.31,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? It's Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.59,0:13:58.14,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:04.70,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, you look completely different with your bangs down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:14.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.49,0:14:15.80,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,is getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.41,0:14:23.40,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.40,0:14:25.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.04,0:14:28.72,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but we should make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:33.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Tooru and Yuuko-chan need their turn, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:37.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're alone in my room right now, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:39.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think they'll be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:43.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be just fine! They get along really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:48.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much! Too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.11,0:15:07.98,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is way too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:08.82,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't feel scared if I close my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.53,0:15:23.94,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.34,0:15:26.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.85,0:15:28.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bath is fr—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:32.18,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yuuko. The bath is free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:36.74,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:38.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.20,0:15:40.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.19,0:15:41.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.79,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Yuuko-chan is—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:44.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:48.50,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was really scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.08,0:15:51.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, a bath. Well, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.33,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.17,0:15:57.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:10.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you ever get scared from not being able to see in front of you while washing your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:18.99,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I was really scared of shampoo—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.82,0:16:25.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got in my eyes—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.41,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:30.25,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the shower?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:37.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.68,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:41.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Please, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:47.90,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:03.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything is all hazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:06.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:09.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an oasis...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.13,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:20.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How was the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:21.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:25.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least turn off the heater.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.86,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to dry our clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:36.16,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really had us worried there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.80,0:17:41.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,They've mostly dried off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:44.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the rain lets up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:47.20,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just keeps coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.66,0:17:52.44,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain makes your hair so hard to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:55.46,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine gets all sticky and clumps together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.46,0:17:59.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine curls up and I can't tie it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:01.73,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we have different types...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:05.03,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yuuko-chan, let me feel your hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.03,0:18:06.49,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.29,0:18:10.22,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Your hair is so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:10.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.71,0:18:14.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:14.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any split ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:17.15,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:38.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't you think these clothes are cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.60,0:18:39.69,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:42.29,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really important part.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:45.23,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.58,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.57,0:18:51.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.02,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:19:00.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.95,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.78,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I overwrite Nagi's records.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.92,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you're so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:15.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fingers are really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.04,0:19:19.91,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you do anything to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.91,0:19:22.38,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.38,0:19:23.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.26,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.26,0:19:33.24,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.81,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's kind of embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.67,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,To-Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.28,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.52,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.61,0:19:50.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:05.04,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like it'll stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:06.97,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,It just keeps coming down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:10.79,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,But I really like the sound of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:11.75,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.95,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I kind of get what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:15.94,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:19.86,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Nagi-chan. Try closing your eyes and listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.86,0:20:21.50,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.50,0:20:22.73,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:24.03,hardsub pos,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:22.00,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. It isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.23,0:21:27.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it kind of sounds like something's sizzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.11,0:21:30.05,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of getting hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:31.59,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.74,0:21:33.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:36.43,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.60,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.16,0:21:39.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.85,0:21:42.09,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful on your way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.09,0:21:43.71,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:45.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:47.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:49.66,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting us over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.85,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that umbrella kind of cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.85,0:21:58.19,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.19,0:22:00.11,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the wind is pretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.11,0:22:02.88,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when the next train is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:08.76,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, you can use the bathroom now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:14.93,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}10 minutes later
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.54,0:22:18.89,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "Be careful."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.74,0:22:21.45,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.45,0:22:23.10,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.61,0:23:56.61,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H9E49D6&\3c&HCACFBF&}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:57.96,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's what you've all been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.96,0:24:01.01,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Yutaka and Miporin will finally appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.01,0:24:02.32,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:04.04,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long, determined, 15-year wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.04,0:24:06.17,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. That's all the flashbacks you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.17,0:24:09.63,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,And didn't you get a scene in the first episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.63,0:24:12.83,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you count that, we're both in the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.83,0:24:14.55,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.55,0:24:17.39,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next A Channel: Classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.39,0:24:22.53,a-ch default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it won't just be us classmates. The upperclassmen will be there too.
